  backgroundDisplayLength: 6
  enableBackgroundZoom: 1
  showTips: 1
  tips:
  - "FloodSafe VR is an immersive virtual reality experience designed to educate
    players on how to respond during a real flood emergency. It puts you in the shoes
    of a flood survivor \u2014 forcing you to make quick decisions, prioritize essential
    supplies, and find a safe escape route.  Built to promote flood preparedness
    and awareness, FloodSafe VR turns critical survival knowledge into an unforgettable
    hands-on experience that stays with you long after you take off the headset."
  - "A flood warning has been issued. The water is rising. Here is what you must
    do:  \U0001F3E0 1. Gather Supplies \u2014 Collect essentials before the water
    gets in  \U0001F6AA 2. Escape the House \u2014 Get out before it's too late 
    \U0001FAB5 3. Find a Floating Object \u2014 Use debris to navigate the flooded
    streets  \U0001F3E2 4. Reach the Tallest Building \u2014 Climb up to safety 
    \U0001F4F1 5. Call for Help \u2014 Get a signal and make the rescue call  Every
    second counts. Every choice matters."
  tipsTitle: Tip
  tipDisplayLength: 6
  requireInputToContinue: 1
  continueText: Continue
